"I have definitely taken advantage of the discounts on CFLs at my local Home Depot and switched out all my old bulbs. I did notice a drop in my utility bill. I plan on installing some of the new LED bulbs and look forward to even more savings. I think it definitely makes sense to conserve energy rather than build new power plants."– Jerry, Batesville, AR 



